-- Apple’s Cook to Be Interviewed on TV, First Time as CEO
-- B y   A d a m   S a t a r i a n o
-- 2012-12-01T00:21:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-01/apple-s-cook-to-be-interviewed-on-tv-first-time-as-ceo.html
Apple Inc. Chief Executive Officer
 Tim Cook  will be interviewed on television for the first time
since taking over the role from Steve Jobs in August 2011.  Cook will be interviewed Dec. 6 on the NBC News program
“Rock Center With Brian Williams” in New York, the network
said in an e-emailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adam Satariano in San Francisco at 
 asatariano1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
